          <text>&lt;html&gt;&lt;body bgcolor="#FFFFFF"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Supporting Families through Addiction Act of 2023&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill directs the Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration to award grants to certain nonprofits to develop or expand services for individuals with substance use disorders and their families.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</text>
